      "default": "<p>We offer a full suite of Shopify eCommerce services from new website builds, design-only projects, and custom app creation to Shopify site takeovers, optimisation advice, and ongoing development support. In our expert hands, youâ€™ll reap the benefits of our design and technical creativity, data-driven decisions, and transparent partnership approach.</p>",
